Wolfgang Puck was born in Austria in 1949. At the age of 16, he moved to the United States and worked at various restaurants before opening his own restaurant, Spago, in Los Angeles in 1982. His other restaurants include Chinois on Main, Cut, and Trattoria del Lupo. Puck has also published several cookbooks, including Wolfgang Puck Cookbook, Wolfgang Puck Express, and Wolfgang Puck Makes It Easy.
